ah-Reid-1920x1080.jpg 1920w, https://adventure.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/Lord-Howe-Island-Woodhen-in-Mt-Gower_s-cloud-forest.1-Image-credit-Sarah-Reid-1180x664.jpg 1180w" sizes="(max-width: 3840) 100vw, 3840" alt="A wood hen in amongst the trees."></div></div>
