<div>
    <article class="columns small-12 medium-6 medium-offset-3">
        <p>During the drive, with crates of olives stacked up behind us, I ask &#x200B;&#x200B;Francesco something I&#x2019;d been dying to ask someone under retirement age who had, like me, swapped the city for the country. Was this a cool, new thing to do or were we just getting old before our time?</p>
<p>&#x201C;I don&#x2019;t think we&#x2019;re getting old!&#x201D; he says. &#x201C;It&#x2019;s definitely not a mass phenomenon, but it&#x2019;s a phenomenon that&#x2019;s becoming noticeable. We are the first generation that grew up with the values and the teachings and the expectations of the &#x2018;90s&#x2026;. You make a lot of money, you have a career, the dream. And our parents, with that dream, destroyed the world.&#x201D;</p>
<p>&#x201C;Then as soon as you get out of high school, you bang your head against the wall,&#x201D; he adds. &#x201C;You go to university then you study finance and you become a doctor, a lawyer. You do all of that and then you don&#x2019;t find a job and it doesn&#x2019;t work.&#x201D;</p>

</article> </div>


<figure>

<div class="row expanded collapse small-up-1 "><img class="gallery " data-lazy-src="https://adventure.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Olive-Oil-katie-mcknoulty-agricola-maraviglia-monte-san-savino-tuscany-olive-mill-pressing-into-oil-0589-1920x1080.jpg" src="https://adventure.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Olive-Oil-katie-mcknoulty-agricola-maraviglia-monte-san-savino-tuscany-olive-mill-pressing-into-oil-0589-1920x1080.jpg" srcset="https://adventure.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Olive-Oil-katie-mcknoulty-agricola-maraviglia-monte-san-savino-tuscany-olive-mill-pressing-into-oil-0589-1920x1080.jpg 1920w, https://adventure.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Olive-Oil-katie-mcknoulty-agricola-maraviglia-monte-san-savino-tuscany-olive-mill-pressing-into-oil-0589-1180x664.jpg 1180w" sizes="(max-width: 3840) 100vw, 3840" alt="Olive can be seen pouring from a vat into a jar."></div><div class="row expanded collapse small-up-1 medium-up-2 img-block-col-2 "><div class="column"><img class="gallery " data-lazy-src="https://adventure.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Olive-Oil-katie-mcknoulty-agricola-maraviglia-monte-san-savino-tuscany-olive-mill-lining-up-to-weigh-olives-0696-1920x1080.jpg" src="https://adventure.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Olive-Oil-katie-mcknoulty-agricola-maraviglia-monte-san-savino-tuscany-olive-mill-lining-up-to-weigh-olives-0696-1920x1080.jpg" srcset="https://adventure.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Olive-Oil-katie-mcknoulty-agricola-maraviglia-monte-san-savino-tuscany-olive-mill-lining-up-to-weigh-olives-0696-1920x1080.jpg 1920w, https://adventure.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Olive-Oil-katie-mcknoulty-agricola-maraviglia-monte-san-savino-tuscany-olive-mill-lining-up-to-weigh-olives-0696-1180x664.jpg 1180w" sizes="(max-width: 3840) 100vw, 3840" alt="A truck at the olive mill lines up to have their olives weighed."></div><div class="column"><img class="gallery " data-lazy-src="https://adventure.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Olive-Oil-katie-mcknoulty-agricola-maraviglia-monte-san-savino-tuscany-olive-mill-0556-1920x1080.jpg" src="https://adventure.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Olive-Oil-katie-mcknoulty-agricola-maraviglia-monte-san-savino-tuscany-olive-mill-0556-1920x1080.jpg" srcset="https://adventure.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Olive-Oil-katie-mcknoulty-agricola-maraviglia-monte-san-savino-tuscany-olive-mill-0556-1920x1080.jpg 1920w, https://adventure.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/Olive-Oil-katie-mcknoulty-agricola-maraviglia-monte-san-savino-tuscany-olive-mill-0556-1180x664.jpg 1180w" sizes="(max-width: 3840) 100vw, 3840" alt="A ute outside the olive mill."></div></div>
